Enum Class Command

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Command>
com.university.utils.commands.Command
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Command>, Constable
public enum Command extends Enum<Command>
The Command enum represents the different commands that a player can execute in the game. Each command has a description and a list of possible aliases, making it easier to interpret user input.
